name: Tick Tock Taxi
description: Online Taxi Booking and iPhone despatch
overview:
Tick Tock Taxi is an innovative young company, here to offer a new solution to booking cabs. Customers can come to our website and get an instant quote for any taxi journey in London, placing the booking there and then. We are in partnership with a large selection of cab companies across the city so that we can compare rates and bring you the best deal. Upon placing your booking, you’ll get a call back directly from the cab office to confirm.

Cab companies and taxi offices can join Tick Tock Taxi to ensure that they reach thousands more people every day, without lifting a finger. We guarantee you a strong online presence, finding customers and passing the bookings directly onto you. Not only do we have the biggest budget for online marketing, but we also have a dedicated team of web development and customer service specialists in house, working hard to bring you more business.
